**Tender Description**
The Canadian Museum of Nature is inviting experienced and qualified firms to submit a proposal in accordance with the attached terms of reference to provide janitorial services at the National Heritage Campus (NHC) in Gatineau, Quebec, in accordance with the attached statement of work.

To submit a bid, please register on the Bonfire website (`https://cmn-mcn.bonfirehub.ca`) and create an online profile. Bid submissions and registration are free of charge. For technical help, call 1-800-354-8010, ext. 2, or submit a request
